OL,3,CNew environment chief vows action on
OL,4,C'unacceptable' river pollution
OL,6,FTackling river pollution is a "top
OL,7,Fpriority", the new Environment
OL,8,FSecretary has said - promising to push
OL,9,Fahead with plans for criminal charges
OL,10,Fagainst water company bosses who fail
OL,11,Fto stop sewage being dumped in UK
OL,12,Fwaterways, and a ban on multi-million
OL,13,Fpound bonuses.
OL,15,FStill only three weeks into his new
OL,16,Fposition heading up the Department for
OL,17,FEnvironment, Food, and Rural Affairs
OL,18,F(Defra), Steve Reed told ITV News
OL,19,FCentral that he's determined to clean
OL,20,Fup the country's rivers.
