OL,3,CNew environment chief vows action on
OL,4,C'unacceptable' river pollution
OL,6,FHe said "Rivers like the Wye and the
OL,7,FSevern are famously awash with toxic
OL,8,Fpollution, including raw human sewage.
OL,9,FThat is unacceptable.
OL,11,F"So water bosses who allow that kind
OL,12,Fof illegal sewage dumping to continue
OL,13,Fwill face criminal charges.
OL,15,F"We will ban the payment of the multi-
OL,16,Fmillion pound bonuses that they're
OL,17,Fawarding themselves.
