OL,6,FBut sewage is only part of the
OL,7,Fproblem. Across the country, the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency estimates that:
OL,10,FMr Reed said his department would be
OL,11,Fworking with farmers to encourage them
OL,12,Fto adopt "more sustainable and nature-
OL,13,Ffriendly" methods of farming, as well
OL,14,Fas using less inorganic fertiliser.
OL,16,FHe said they would also encourage the
OL,17,Fuse of "natural barriers" to try to
OL,18,Fprevent run-off from fields ending up
OL,19,Fin rivers.
