OL,3,CNew environment chief vows action on
OL,4,C'unacceptable' river pollution
OL,6,FHe said "Over time, we can clean up
OL,7,Four rivers - and that is what this
OL,8,Fgovernment intends to do".
OL,10,FAnd while they try, they will have an
OL,11,Farmy of campaigners and citizen
OL,12,Fscientists across the country
OL,13,Fmonitoring their progress.
OL,15,FThe Angling Trust first launched its
OL,16,Fown Water Quality Monitoring Network
OL,17,Fin 2022, following an ITV Central
OL,18,Finvestigation which revealed dangerous
OL,19,Flevels of toxic chemicals in rivers
OL,20,Facross the Midlands.
