OL,6,FIt began on the River Severn, before
OL,7,Fbeing rolled out nationwide - and
OL,8,Fhundreds of anglers have now signed
OL,9,Fup, regularly testing waterways up and
OL,10,Fdown the country.
OL,12,FSimilar schemes have been launched by
OL,13,Fother environmental groups too,
OL,14,Fregularly recording of phosphates,
OL,15,Fnitrates, and other toxins, far above
OL,16,Fthe levels deemed safe by experts.
OL,18,F"People want change"
OL,20,FMr Reed said "People are furious.
