OL,6,F"If they live near a polluted river or
OL,7,Fthe sea, and they can't take their
OL,8,Fkids in there any more, they're really
OL,9,Fangry because they remember when they
OL,10,Fwere younger, they could go and paddle
OL,11,Faround in the water and kids loved it
OL,12,F- but they're worried that their kids
OL,13,Fwill get sick. So people want change."
